{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"One thing the world needs,"},{"time":4000,"text":"one thing this country desperately needs"},{"time":6000,"text":"is a better way"},{"time":8000,"text":"of conducting our political debates."},{"time":10000,"text":"We need to rediscover"},{"time":12000,"text":"the lost art of democratic argument."},{"time":15000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":21000,"text":"If you think about the arguments we have,"},{"time":24000,"text":"most of the time it's shouting matches"},{"time":26000,"text":"on cable television,"},{"time":28000,"text":"ideological food fights on the floor of Congress."},{"time":33000,"text":"I have a suggestion."},{"time":35000,"text":"Look at all the arguments we have these days"},{"time":38000,"text":"over health care,"},{"time":40000,"text":"over bonuses and bailouts on Wall Street,"},{"time":43000,"text":"over the gap between rich and poor,"},{"time":46000,"text":"over affirmative action and same-sex marriage."},{"time":49000,"text":"Lying just beneath the surface"},{"time":51000,"text":"of those arguments,"},{"time":54000,"text":"with passions raging on all sides,"},{"time":57000,"text":"are big questions"},{"time":60000,"text":"of moral philosophy,"},{"time":62000,"text":"big questions of justice."},{"time":64000,"text":"But we too rarely"},{"time":66000,"text":"articulate and defend"},{"time":69000,"text":"and argue about"},{"time":71000,"text":"those big moral questions in our politics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"So what I would like to do today"},{"time":77000,"text":"is have something of a discussion."},{"time":79000,"text":"First, let me take"},{"time":81000,"text":"a famous philosopher"},{"time":83000,"text":"who wrote about those questions"},{"time":85000,"text":"of justice and morality,"},{"time":87000,"text":"give you a very short lecture"},{"time":89000,"text":"on Aristotle of ancient Athens,"},{"time":92000,"text":"Aristotle's theory of justice,"},{"time":94000,"text":"and then have a discussion here"},{"time":97000,"text":"to see whether Aristotle's ideas"},{"time":99000,"text":"actually inform"},{"time":101000,"text":"the way we think and argue"},{"time":103000,"text":"about questions today."},{"time":106000,"text":"So, are you ready for the lecture?"},{"time":110000,"text":"According to Aristotle,"},{"time":112000,"text":"justice means giving people what they deserve."},{"time":118000,"text":"That's it; that's the lecture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":120000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":123000,"text":"Now, you may say, well, that's obvious enough."},{"time":125000,"text":"The real questions begin"},{"time":127000,"text":"when it comes to arguing about"},{"time":129000,"text":"who deserves what and why."},{"time":133000,"text":"Take the example of flutes."},{"time":135000,"text":"Suppose we're distributing flutes."},{"time":138000,"text":"Who should get the best ones?"},{"time":140000,"text":"Let's see what people --"},{"time":142000,"text":"What would you say?"},{"time":144000,"text":"Who should get the best flute?"},{"time":146000,"text":"You can just call it out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148000,"text":"(Audience: Random.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":150000,"text":"Michael Sandel: At random. You would do it by lottery."},{"time":152000,"text":"Or by the first person to rush into the hall to get them."},{"time":156000,"text":"Who else?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"(Audience: The best flute players.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160000,"text":"MS: The best flute players. (Audience: The worst flute players.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"MS: The worst flute players."},{"time":165000,"text":"How many say the best flute players?"},{"time":169000,"text":"Why?"},{"time":172000,"text":"Actually, that was Aristotle's answer too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":177000,"text":"But here's a harder question."},{"time":179000,"text":"Why do you think,"},{"time":181000,"text":"those of you who voted this way,"},{"time":183000,"text":"that the best flutes should go to the best flute players?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"Peter: The greatest benefit to all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188000,"text":"MS: The greatest benefit to all."},{"time":190000,"text":"We'll hear better music"},{"time":192000,"text":"if the best flutes should go to the best flute players."},{"time":195000,"text":"That's Peter? (Audience: Peter.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197000,"text":"MS: All right."},{"time":200000,"text":"Well, it's a good reason."},{"time":202000,"text":"We'll all be better off if good music is played"},{"time":204000,"text":"rather than terrible music."},{"time":208000,"text":"But Peter,"},{"time":210000,"text":"Aristotle doesn't agree with you that that's the reason."},{"time":213000,"text":"That's all right."},{"time":215000,"text":"Aristotle had a different reason"},{"time":217000,"text":"for saying the best flutes should go to the best flute players."},{"time":220000,"text":"He said,"},{"time":222000,"text":"that's what flutes are for --"},{"time":224000,"text":"to be played well."},{"time":227000,"text":"He says that to reason about"},{"time":229000,"text":"just distribution of a thing,"},{"time":232000,"text":"we have to reason about,"},{"time":235000,"text":"and sometimes argue about,"},{"time":237000,"text":"the purpose of the thing,"},{"time":239000,"text":"or the social activity --"},{"time":241000,"text":"in this case, musical performance."},{"time":243000,"text":"And the point, the essential nature,"},{"time":245000,"text":"of musical performance"},{"time":247000,"text":"is to produce excellent music."},{"time":249000,"text":"It'll be a happy byproduct"},{"time":251000,"text":"that we'll all benefit."},{"time":255000,"text":"But when we think about justice,"},{"time":258000,"text":"Aristotle says,"},{"time":260000,"text":"what we really need to think about"},{"time":262000,"text":"is the essential nature of the activity in question"},{"time":266000,"text":"and the qualities that are worth"},{"time":269000,"text":"honoring and admiring and recognizing."},{"time":272000,"text":"One of the reasons"},{"time":274000,"text":"that the best flute players should get the best flutes"},{"time":276000,"text":"is that musical performance"},{"time":278000,"text":"is not only to make the rest of us happy,"},{"time":280000,"text":"but to honor"},{"time":282000,"text":"and recognize"},{"time":284000,"text":"the excellence"},{"time":286000,"text":"of the best musicians."}]},{"cues":[{"time":288000,"text":"Now, flutes may seem ... the distribution of flutes"},{"time":291000,"text":"may seem a trivial case."},{"time":294000,"text":"Let's take a contemporary example"},{"time":296000,"text":"of the dispute about justice."},{"time":299000,"text":"It had to do with golf."},{"time":301000,"text":"Casey Martin -- a few years ago,"},{"time":303000,"text":"Casey Martin --"},{"time":305000,"text":"did any of you hear about him?"},{"time":307000,"text":"He was a very good golfer,"},{"time":309000,"text":"but he had a disability."},{"time":311000,"text":"He had a bad leg, a circulatory problem,"},{"time":314000,"text":"that made it very painful"},{"time":316000,"text":"for him to walk the course."},{"time":319000,"text":"In fact, it carried risk of injury."},{"time":323000,"text":"He asked the PGA,"},{"time":325000,"text":"the Professional Golfers' Association,"},{"time":327000,"text":"for permission to use a golf cart"},{"time":330000,"text":"in the PGA tournaments."},{"time":332000,"text":"They said, \"No."},{"time":334000,"text":"Now that would give you an unfair advantage.\""},{"time":336000,"text":"He sued,"},{"time":338000,"text":"and his case went all the way"},{"time":340000,"text":"to the Supreme Court, believe it or not,"},{"time":342000,"text":"the case over the golf cart,"},{"time":345000,"text":"because the law says"},{"time":347000,"text":"that the disabled"},{"time":349000,"text":"must be accommodated,"},{"time":352000,"text":"provided the accommodation does not"},{"time":355000,"text":"change the essential nature"},{"time":358000,"text":"of the activity."},{"time":360000,"text":"He says, \"I'm a great golfer."},{"time":362000,"text":"I want to compete."},{"time":364000,"text":"But I need a golf cart"},{"time":366000,"text":"to get from one hole to the next.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"Suppose you were"},{"time":370000,"text":"on the Supreme Court."},{"time":372000,"text":"Suppose you were deciding"},{"time":374000,"text":"the justice of this case."},{"time":377000,"text":"How many here would say"},{"time":379000,"text":"that Casey Martin does have a right to use a golf cart?"},{"time":382000,"text":"And how many say, no, he doesn't?"},{"time":386000,"text":"All right, let's take a poll, show of hands."},{"time":388000,"text":"How many would rule in favor of Casey Martin?"},{"time":392000,"text":"And how many would not? How many would say he doesn't?"},{"time":395000,"text":"All right, we have a good division of opinion here."},{"time":399000,"text":"Someone who would not"},{"time":401000,"text":"grant Casey Martin the right to a golf cart,"},{"time":403000,"text":"what would be your reason?"},{"time":405000,"text":"Raise your hand, and we'll try to get you a microphone."},{"time":407000,"text":"What would be your reason?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":410000,"text":"(Audience: It'd be an unfair advantage.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412000,"text":"MS: It would be an unfair advantage"},{"time":415000,"text":"if he gets to ride in a golf cart."},{"time":417000,"text":"All right, those of you,"},{"time":419000,"text":"I imagine most of you who would not give him the golf cart"},{"time":422000,"text":"worry about an unfair advantage."},{"time":424000,"text":"What about those of you who say"},{"time":426000,"text":"he should be given a golf cart?"},{"time":428000,"text":"How would you answer the objection?"},{"time":430000,"text":"Yes, all right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":432000,"text":"Audience: The cart's not part of the game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"MS: What's your name? (Audience: Charlie.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":438000,"text":"MS: Charlie says --"},{"time":441000,"text":"We'll get Charlie a microphone in case someone wants to reply."},{"time":443000,"text":"Tell us, Charlie,"},{"time":445000,"text":"why would you say he should be able to use a golf cart?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"Charlie: The cart's not part of the game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452000,"text":"MS: But what about walking from hole to hole?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455000,"text":"Charlie: It doesn't matter; it's not part of the game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":458000,"text":"MS: Walking the course is not part of the game of golf?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462000,"text":"Charlie: Not in my book, it isn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464000,"text":"MS: All right. Stay there, Charlie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":468000,"text":"Who has an answer for Charlie?"},{"time":471000,"text":"All right, who has an answer for Charlie?"},{"time":473000,"text":"What would you say?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":475000,"text":"Audience: The endurance element is a very important part of the game,"},{"time":478000,"text":"walking all those holes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"MS: Walking all those holes?"},{"time":482000,"text":"That's part of the game of golf? (Audience: Absolutely.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":485000,"text":"MS: What's your name? (Audience: Warren.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"MS: Warren."},{"time":490000,"text":"Charlie, what do you say to Warren?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494000,"text":"Charley: I'll stick to my original thesis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"MS: Warren, are you a golfer?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"Warren: I am not a golfer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":506000,"text":"Charley: And I am. (MS: Okay.)"},{"time":508000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":510000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":514000,"text":"You know,"},{"time":516000,"text":"it's interesting."},{"time":520000,"text":"In the case, in the lower court,"},{"time":522000,"text":"they brought in golfing greats"},{"time":525000,"text":"to testify on this very issue."},{"time":529000,"text":"Is walking the course essential to the game?"},{"time":532000,"text":"And they brought in Jack Nicklaus and Arnold Palmer."},{"time":535000,"text":"And what do you suppose they all said?"},{"time":537000,"text":"Yes. They agreed with Warren."},{"time":540000,"text":"They said, yes, walking the course"},{"time":542000,"text":"is strenuous physical exercise."},{"time":544000,"text":"The fatigue factor is an important part of golf."},{"time":547000,"text":"And so it would change"},{"time":549000,"text":"the fundamental nature of the game"},{"time":552000,"text":"to give him the golf cart."},{"time":554000,"text":"Now, notice,"},{"time":556000,"text":"something interesting --"},{"time":558000,"text":"Well, I should tell you about the Supreme Court first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560000,"text":"The Supreme Court"},{"time":562000,"text":"decided."},{"time":564000,"text":"What do you suppose they said?"},{"time":567000,"text":"They said yes,"},{"time":569000,"text":"that Casey Martin must be provided a golf cart."},{"time":572000,"text":"Seven to two, they ruled."},{"time":575000,"text":"What was interesting about their ruling"},{"time":579000,"text":"and about the discussion we've just had"},{"time":583000,"text":"is that the discussion about"},{"time":585000,"text":"the right, the justice, of the matter"},{"time":587000,"text":"depended on"},{"time":589000,"text":"figuring out what is"},{"time":592000,"text":"the essential nature of golf."},{"time":595000,"text":"And the Supreme Court justices"},{"time":597000,"text":"wrestled with that question."},{"time":599000,"text":"And Justice Stevens, writing for the majority,"},{"time":601000,"text":"said he had read all about the history of golf,"},{"time":606000,"text":"and the essential point of the game"},{"time":609000,"text":"is to get very small ball from one place"},{"time":611000,"text":"into a hole"},{"time":613000,"text":"in as few strokes as possible,"},{"time":616000,"text":"and that walking was not essential, but incidental."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618000,"text":"Now, there were two dissenters,"},{"time":620000,"text":"one of whom was Justice Scalia."},{"time":625000,"text":"He wouldn't have granted the cart,"},{"time":628000,"text":"and he had a very interesting dissent."},{"time":630000,"text":"It's interesting because"},{"time":632000,"text":"he rejected the Aristotelian premise"},{"time":635000,"text":"underlying the majority's opinion."},{"time":637000,"text":"He said it's not possible"},{"time":640000,"text":"to determine the essential nature"},{"time":643000,"text":"of a game like golf."},{"time":645000,"text":"Here's how he put it."},{"time":647000,"text":"\"To say that something is essential"},{"time":649000,"text":"is ordinarily to say that it is necessary"},{"time":651000,"text":"to the achievement of a certain object."},{"time":654000,"text":"But since it is the very nature of a game"},{"time":656000,"text":"to have no object except amusement,"},{"time":660000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":664000,"text":"that is, what distinguishes games"},{"time":666000,"text":"from productive activity,"},{"time":668000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":671000,"text":"it is quite impossible to say"},{"time":673000,"text":"that any of a game's arbitrary rules"},{"time":676000,"text":"is essential.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":678000,"text":"So there you have Justice Scalia"},{"time":680000,"text":"taking on the Aristotelian premise"},{"time":683000,"text":"of the majority's opinion."},{"time":686000,"text":"Justice Scalia's opinion"},{"time":689000,"text":"is questionable"},{"time":691000,"text":"for two reasons."},{"time":693000,"text":"First, no real sports fan would talk that way."},{"time":696000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":698000,"text":"If we had thought that the rules"},{"time":700000,"text":"of the sports we care about"},{"time":702000,"text":"are merely arbitrary,"},{"time":704000,"text":"rather than designed to call forth"},{"time":707000,"text":"the virtues and the excellences"},{"time":710000,"text":"that we think are worthy of admiring,"},{"time":712000,"text":"we wouldn't care about the outcome of the game."},{"time":715000,"text":"It's also objectionable"},{"time":718000,"text":"on a second ground."},{"time":720000,"text":"On the face of it,"},{"time":722000,"text":"it seemed to be -- this debate about the golf cart --"},{"time":725000,"text":"an argument about fairness,"},{"time":728000,"text":"what's an unfair advantage."},{"time":732000,"text":"But if fairness were the only thing at stake,"},{"time":735000,"text":"there would have been an easy and obvious solution."},{"time":738000,"text":"What would it be? (Audience: Let everyone use the cart.)"},{"time":740000,"text":"Let everyone ride in a golf cart"},{"time":743000,"text":"if they want to."},{"time":745000,"text":"Then the fairness objection goes away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748000,"text":"But letting everyone ride in a cart"},{"time":751000,"text":"would have been, I suspect,"},{"time":753000,"text":"more anathema"},{"time":755000,"text":"to the golfing greats"},{"time":757000,"text":"and to the PGA,"},{"time":759000,"text":"even than making an exception for Casey Martin."},{"time":761000,"text":"Why?"},{"time":763000,"text":"Because what was at stake"},{"time":765000,"text":"in the dispute over the golf cart"},{"time":768000,"text":"was not only the essential nature of golf,"},{"time":771000,"text":"but, relatedly, the question:"},{"time":774000,"text":"What abilities"},{"time":777000,"text":"are worthy"},{"time":779000,"text":"of honor and recognition"},{"time":781000,"text":"as athletic talents?"},{"time":784000,"text":"Let me put the point"},{"time":786000,"text":"as delicately as possible:"},{"time":789000,"text":"Golfers are a little sensitive"},{"time":791000,"text":"about the athletic status of their game."},{"time":794000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":800000,"text":"After all, there's no running or jumping,"},{"time":803000,"text":"and the ball stands still."},{"time":806000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":809000,"text":"So if golfing is the kind of game"},{"time":812000,"text":"that can be played while riding around in a golf cart,"},{"time":815000,"text":"it would be hard to confer"},{"time":818000,"text":"on the golfing greats"},{"time":820000,"text":"the status that we confer,"},{"time":822000,"text":"the honor and recognition"},{"time":824000,"text":"that goes to truly great athletes."},{"time":828000,"text":"That illustrates"},{"time":831000,"text":"that with golf,"},{"time":834000,"text":"as with flutes,"},{"time":836000,"text":"it's hard to decide the question"},{"time":839000,"text":"of what justice requires,"},{"time":842000,"text":"without grappling with the question,"},{"time":844000,"text":"\"What is the essential nature"},{"time":846000,"text":"of the activity in question,"},{"time":848000,"text":"and what qualities,"},{"time":851000,"text":"what excellences"},{"time":853000,"text":"connected with that activity,"},{"time":855000,"text":"are worthy of honor and recognition?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":859000,"text":"Let's take a final example"},{"time":861000,"text":"that's prominent in contemporary political debate:"},{"time":864000,"text":"same-sex marriage."},{"time":868000,"text":"There are those who favor state recognition"},{"time":871000,"text":"only of traditional marriage"},{"time":873000,"text":"between one man and one woman,"},{"time":876000,"text":"and there are those who favor state recognition"},{"time":878000,"text":"of same-sex marriage."},{"time":880000,"text":"How many here"},{"time":882000,"text":"favor the first policy:"},{"time":884000,"text":"the state should recognize traditional marriage only?"},{"time":889000,"text":"And how many favor the second, same-sex marriage?"},{"time":893000,"text":"Now, put it this way:"},{"time":896000,"text":"What ways of thinking"},{"time":898000,"text":"about justice and morality"},{"time":900000,"text":"underlie the arguments we have"},{"time":902000,"text":"over marriage?"},{"time":904000,"text":"The opponents of same-sex marriage say"},{"time":907000,"text":"that the purpose of marriage,"},{"time":909000,"text":"fundamentally, is procreation,"},{"time":911000,"text":"and that's what's worthy of honoring"},{"time":913000,"text":"and recognizing and encouraging."},{"time":916000,"text":"And the defenders of same-sex marriage say no,"},{"time":919000,"text":"procreation is not the only purpose of marriage;"},{"time":923000,"text":"what about a lifelong, mutual, loving commitment?"},{"time":926000,"text":"That's really what marriage is about."},{"time":930000,"text":"So with flutes, with golf carts,"},{"time":933000,"text":"and even with a fiercely contested question"},{"time":936000,"text":"like same-sex marriage,"},{"time":939000,"text":"Aristotle has a point."},{"time":942000,"text":"Very hard to argue about justice"},{"time":944000,"text":"without first arguing"},{"time":947000,"text":"about the purpose of social institutions"},{"time":950000,"text":"and about what qualities are worthy"},{"time":952000,"text":"of honor and recognition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":955000,"text":"So let's step back from these cases"},{"time":958000,"text":"and see how they shed light"},{"time":961000,"text":"on the way we might improve, elevate,"},{"time":964000,"text":"the terms of political discourse"},{"time":967000,"text":"in the United States,"},{"time":969000,"text":"and for that matter, around the world."},{"time":972000,"text":"There is a tendency to think"},{"time":974000,"text":"that if we engage too directly"},{"time":977000,"text":"with moral questions in politics,"},{"time":979000,"text":"that's a recipe for disagreement,"},{"time":981000,"text":"and for that matter, a recipe for"},{"time":983000,"text":"intolerance and coercion."},{"time":985000,"text":"So better to shy away from,"},{"time":987000,"text":"to ignore,"},{"time":989000,"text":"the moral and the religious convictions"},{"time":991000,"text":"that people bring to civic life."},{"time":993000,"text":"It seems to me that our discussion"},{"time":996000,"text":"reflects the opposite,"},{"time":998000,"text":"that a better way"},{"time":1001000,"text":"to mutual respect"},{"time":1003000,"text":"is to engage directly"},{"time":1005000,"text":"with the moral convictions"},{"time":1007000,"text":"citizens bring to public life,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"rather than to require"},{"time":1012000,"text":"that people leave their deepest moral convictions"},{"time":1015000,"text":"outside politics"},{"time":1017000,"text":"before they enter."},{"time":1019000,"text":"That, it seems to me, is a way"},{"time":1021000,"text":"to begin to restore"},{"time":1023000,"text":"the art of democratic argument."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1025000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1027000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1030000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1032000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1037000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1039000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":1041000,"text":"Thanks. Thank you."},{"time":1044000,"text":"Chris."},{"time":1046000,"text":"Thanks, Chris."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1049000,"text":"Chris Anderson: From flutes to golf courses"},{"time":1051000,"text":"to same-sex marriage --"},{"time":1053000,"text":"that was a genius link."},{"time":1055000,"text":"Now look, you're a pioneer of open education."},{"time":1058000,"text":"Your lecture series was one of the first to do it big."},{"time":1060000,"text":"What's your vision for the next phase of this?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1063000,"text":"MS: Well, I think that it is possible."},{"time":1066000,"text":"In the classroom, we have arguments"},{"time":1069000,"text":"on some of the most fiercely held"},{"time":1072000,"text":"moral convictions that students have"},{"time":1074000,"text":"about big public questions."},{"time":1076000,"text":"And I think we can do that in public life more generally."},{"time":1079000,"text":"And so my real dream would be"},{"time":1081000,"text":"to take the public television series"},{"time":1083000,"text":"that we've created of the course --"},{"time":1085000,"text":"it's available now, online,"},{"time":1087000,"text":"free for everyone anywhere in the world --"},{"time":1089000,"text":"and to see whether we can partner with institutions,"},{"time":1092000,"text":"at universities in China, in India,"},{"time":1094000,"text":"in Africa, around the world,"},{"time":1096000,"text":"to try to promote"},{"time":1099000,"text":"civic education"},{"time":1101000,"text":"and also a richer kind"},{"time":1103000,"text":"of democratic debate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1106000,"text":"CA: So you picture, at some point,"},{"time":1108000,"text":"live, in real time,"},{"time":1110000,"text":"you could have this kind of conversation, inviting questions,"},{"time":1113000,"text":"but with people from China and India joining in?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1116000,"text":"MS: Right. We did a little bit of it here"},{"time":1118000,"text":"with 1,500 people in Long Beach,"},{"time":1120000,"text":"and we do it in a classroom at Harvard"},{"time":1123000,"text":"with about 1,000 students."},{"time":1125000,"text":"Wouldn't it be interesting"},{"time":1127000,"text":"to take this way"},{"time":1130000,"text":"of thinking and arguing,"},{"time":1132000,"text":"engaging seriously with big moral questions,"},{"time":1135000,"text":"exploring cultural differences"},{"time":1137000,"text":"and connect through a live video hookup,"},{"time":1141000,"text":"students in Beijing and Mumbai"},{"time":1143000,"text":"and in Cambridge, Massachusetts"},{"time":1145000,"text":"and create a global classroom."},{"time":1147000,"text":"That's what I would love to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1149000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153000,"text":"CA: So, I would imagine"},{"time":1155000,"text":"that there are a lot of people who would love to join you in that endeavor."},{"time":1158000,"text":"Michael Sandel. Thank you so much. (MS: Thanks so much.)"}]}]}